        "text_eGXbBJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Solving Fit & Reducing Returns: Your feet are 3-dimensional. So are your shoes. Yet, today shoe sizing is still based on length and width. It’s no wonder 30-40% of footwear orders online are returned. But, it doesn’t have to be this way. Aetrex’s FitAI™ footwear recommendations software custom recommends and matches footwear to individuals based on their unique 3D foot scan data and information.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
