            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "text_KhVqYe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>FitStarter is a personalized footwear recommendation platform designed to help retailers improve their shoe fitting service for shoppers, reduce returns, and increase customer satisfaction. Developed in partnership with the premier shoe fit testing company Heeluxe, FitStarter is an accurate, turnkey starting point to Aetrex’s AI-powered shoe match-making platform, FitGenius.<br/><br/>Aetrex utilizes its own Fit Labs to analyze shoes submitted by participating retailers each season using the patented Heeluxe technology, which utilizes PSI pressure sensors. The FitStarter platform analyzes each customer’s unique 3D foot scan data collected in store, from either an AlbertPro or Albert 3D Fit, alongside the Fit Lab data to provide immediate, personalized fitting recommendations. Within days, retailers can have customized footwear and fit recommendations available in their stores.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
